  sense
    part_of_speech noun
    gloss "A statement (in domain specific terms) which specifies a verifiable constraint on an implementation that it shall undeniably meet or (a) be deemed unacceptable, or (b) result in implementation failure, or (c) result in system failure."
    provenance (wiktionary)
